{
  "stem": "27687.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Were they what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were not abusive to me, actually, but they were abusive to these little animals, because he said that in school they were taught that when they rip out the tail, the tail will regrow, you see.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so he ripped out-- he caught some of these little animals and ripped out the tail.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said to him, oh, boy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What if that hurts for that little-- he said, who are you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were the, you know, you have to learn a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have to be prepared for a war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was in 1936.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happens next.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, what next happened was the time when the Germans made the first pogrom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was in 1938.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1938, they made a Kristallnacht, because they said that a Jew in Paris-- his name was Grynszpan-- was killing one of the German ambassadors.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How-- it was right in the paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I read it in the paper, and the next day-- and the next day there was a pogrom.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came and they broke in the houses, and they broke everything possible and they took--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--father away.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they wanted to take my me away, but the police what was there said to the people from the party, the SA, not the SS, but that was the SA with the brown shirts, and day said to him, they said, no, no, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We cannot take him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He is not 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He is only 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You cannot take him, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they left me, but they took my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father went to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
